Package: pivotprobs
Type: Package
Title: Methods for estimating the probability of pivot events in election models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Eggers", "Andy", email = "aeggers@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Andy Eggers <aeggers@gmail.com>
Description: For studying strategic voting, voting paradoxes, and voting weights, it is useful to compute the probability of pivot events. This package contains several methods for computing pivot event probabilities in common voting systems given a model of election outcomes.
